## Overview

**{{ org.name }}** has **{{ rules.total_count }} D&R rules** across {{ rules.categories | length }} categories{% if managed_packs %}, plus {{ managed_packs | length }} managed rule pack(s){% endif %}. Of these, **{{ rules.enabled_count }} are enabled** and **{{ rules.disabled_count }} are disabled** (awaiting human review).

| State | Meaning |
|-------|---------|
| **Enabled** | Actively evaluated against incoming telemetry |
| **Disabled** | Deployed but not evaluated; typically awaiting human review |

