<details>
<summary><strong>CLI Commands Reference</strong></summary>

```bash
# List all D&R rules
limacharlie dr list --oid {{ org.oid }} --output yaml

# Get a specific rule's full definition
limacharlie dr get --key "<rule-name>" --oid {{ org.oid }} --output yaml

# Enable a disabled rule (after review)
limacharlie dr set --name "<rule-name>" --enabled true --oid {{ org.oid }}

# List FP rules
limacharlie dr fp list --oid {{ org.oid }} --output yaml

# Validate a new rule before deploying
limacharlie dr validate --detect detect.yaml --respond respond.yaml --oid {{ org.oid }}
```

</details>

